paragraph: Dan Maines (born March 10, 1971) is the bassist for the hard rock band Clutch. He is also the bassist for an instrumental side project, The Bakerton Group. Dan Maines has remained the bassist for Clutch since the group started in 1990.
Lakland 44-64 ( P bass with a Jazz neck) with a dark star pickup
Fender custom shop 1961 closet classic jazz bass 2011 black
Ampeg SVT CL for most of the albums
Ampeg SVT VR for Strange Cousins From The West
